                <statement>
                    <p>
                        The set of values <m>\lrbrace{(x,y)\mid f(x,y)\text{ exists}}</m> is called the
                        <ol marker="A." cols="2">
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    Range
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    Inputs
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>
